                            <br><br>
                            <a href="https://twitter.com/share" class="twitter-share-button" data-url="<%= SlackSup::Service.url %>" data-text="The most valuable relationships are not made of two people, they’re made of three." data-via="playplayio" data-size="large" data-related="SlackAPI">Tweet</a>
